Description: 
Adguard 6.3.1399.4073 Final + Repack + Portable 1.5.8 (455) MacOSX Adguard is one of the famous applications of the developer of software products company Insoft, designed to block advertising banners and pop-up windows when working on the Internet.This utility supports filtering when working with browsers such as Internet Explorer, Google Chrome, Mozilla Firefox, Safari, Opera, Maxthon, Avant Browser, Netscape Navigator, Flock, Lunascape, K-Melon, GreenBrower, Orca, MyIE, ComodoDragon, SeaMonkey, SRWare Iron, Rale Moon. Adguard belongs to the family of Adblock programs, the main task of which is to control the quality of operation of web resources and the Internet as a whole.Among other things, Adguard has low memory consumption, integration with WoT is a separate extension that can be disabled, there is support for CSS injection rules, it is possible to edit the source code of user scripts (updates are checked only with included user scripts), setting exceptions for filtering protected ( HTTPS) sites.Note that Adguard is a reliable addition to the basic anti-virus protection with effective blocking of malicious, fraudulent and phishing resources, and parental control over the online activity of children.
